emember%20the%20game%20for%20the%20Commodore%0A64%20called%20The%20Eidolon%3F%20It%20was%20great.%20Three%20eggcups%20sang%20%22Oh%20Mr%20Sandman%22%0Ato%20you.%20Dragons%20and%20everything.%20Cool.%3C%2Ffont%3E%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%0A%0A%3Cli%3E%0A%3Cb%3E%3Cfont%20face%3D%22Arial%2CHelvetica%22%3EWhile%20I'm%20about%20it%2C%20can%20you%20sort%20something%0Aout%20for%20me%3F%20I%20distinctly%20remember%20a%20character%20called%20the%20%22Naughty%20Torty%22.%0AThe%20idea%20behind%20the%20Naughty%20Torty%20was%20that%20he%20was%20a%20six%20foot%20tall%20tortoise%0Awho%20walked%20into%20a%20crowd%20of%20children%20and%20vomited%20on%20them.%20His%20keeper%2C%20a%0Aman%20with%20a%20tortoise%20training%20whip%2C%20would%20then%20run%20on%2C%20shouting%20%22No!%20Naughty%0ATorty!%22.%20He%20would%20then%20usher%20the%20tortoise%2C%20who%20was%20still%20holding%20his%20tummy%0Aand%20looking%20rather%20poorly%2C%20off%20stage.%20Did%20this%20really%20happen%3F%20Or%20did%20I%0Amake%20it%20up%20and%20believe%20myself%3F%3C%2Ffont%3E%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%0A%0A%3Cli%3E%0A%3Cb%3E%3Cfont%20face%3D%22Arial%2CHelvetica%22%3EOh%20yeah%20-%20don't%20flush%20the%20toilet.%20Due%20to%0Aa%20wiring%20problem%2C%20the%20lever%20that%20looks%20like%20it%20should%20flush%20the%20toilet%0Aactually%20releases%20purple%20knockout%20gas.%20God%20knows%20where%20the%20lever%20that%20actually%0Aflushes%20the%20toilet%20is.%20Or%2C%20indeed%2C%20what%20purple%20knockout%20gas%20is%20doing%20on%0Aboard%20a%20passenger%20flight%20to%20Venus.%3C%2Ffont%3E%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%0A%0A%3Cli%3E%0A%3Cb%3E%3Cfont%20face%3D%22Arial%2CHelvetica%22%3ENaughty%20Torty%20dilemma%20solved!%20According%20to%20Josie%0ARogers%20and%20S%20D%20Birks%2C%20he%20appeared%20on%20Saturday%20Morning%20TV%20Show%20%22What's%20Up%0ADoc%3F%22%20with%20Andy%20Crane%20and%20the%20bloke%20from%20the%20Twix%20adverts%2C%20who%20apparently%0Ahad%20a%20profound%20love%20of%20cheese.%20And%20do%20you%20know%20what%20he%20vomited%20on%20the%20children%3F%0AThat's%20right!%20It%20was%20ghee!%20All%20you've%20got%20to%20remember%20now%20is%20the%20singing%20eggcups%0Afrom%20The%20Eidolon%20and%20my%20history%20will%20be%20complete..%3C%2Ffont%3E%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%0A%3C%2Ful%3E%0A%0A%3Ctable%20border%3D%220%22%20cols%3D%222%22%20width%3D%22100%25%22%3E%0A%3Ctbody%3E%3Ctr%3E%0A%3Ctd%3E%0A%3Cdiv%20align%3D%22right%22%3E%3Cimg%20border%3D%220%22%20height%3D%2278%22%20width%3D%22120%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%0A%3C%2Ftd%3E%0A%0A%3Ctd%3E%3Cfont%20color%3D%22%23FFCC99%22%3E%3Cfont%20size%3D%22%2B1%22%3EThese%20pages%20are%20sponsored%20by%20Julian%0Aand%20Sandy%2C%20the%20Alien%20Fingers%20from%20Pluto.%20They%20wish%20you%20a%20nice%20space%20day.%0AThat's%20the%20equivalent%20of%20three%20Earth%20days%2C%20and%20is%20therefore%20exceptionally%0Apolite.%3C%2Ffont%3E%3C%2Ffont%3E%3C%2Ftd%3E%0A%3C%2Ftr%3E%0A%3C%2Ftbody%3E%3C%2Ftable%3E%0A%0A%0A%0A%3C%2Fbody%3E%0A%3C%2Fbody%3E%0A%3C%2Fhtml%3E"
